<p>
We got your <%= "receipt".pluralize(@receipts_count) %>, thanks! <%= "You can find #{@receipts_count == 1 ? "it" : "them"} in your #{link_to "Receipt Bin", my_inbox_url}.".html_safe unless @receipts_count == @pairs.size %>
</p>

<% if @pairs.size > 0 %>
  <p>We also automatically matched <%= @receipts_count == 1 ? "it" : "#{@pairs.size} #{"receipt".pluralize(@pairs.size)}"%> to the following <%= "transaction".pluralize(@pairs.size) %>:</p>

  <ul>
    <% @pairs.map do |pair| %>
      <li><%= link_to pair.memo, hcb_code_url(pair) %> from <%= time_ago_in_words pair.pt&.raw_pending_stripe_transaction&.created_at || Time.at(pair.raw_stripe_transaction.stripe_transaction["created"]) %> ago</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <p>Did we get something wrong? You can remove an incorrect receipt on the transaction's page.</p>
<% end %>

<p>
  From,<br>
  The HCB Team
</p>
